
This script will create averaged cti trend data and plots for monthly report. 
Set the following environment first:

setenv PYTHONPATH "/data/mta/Script/Python3.6/envs/ska3/lib/python3.6/site-packages:/data/mta/Script/Python3.6/lib/python3.6/site-packages/"

then simply run:

    monthly_report_cti_avg_plots_two_section.py

Input: /data/mta/Script/ACIS/CTI/Data/*/*
Output: 
    ./Plots/cti_avg_acis_bi.png
    ./Plots/cti_avg_acis_i.png
    ./Plots/cti_avg_acis_s.png

    ./Data/cti_data/ccd<ccd>_data


Note, the plots are also used by the main CTI page.
